<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Confirmation</title>
    <style>
        body {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
        }

        h2 {
            font-size: 30px;
        }

        .container {
            position: relative;
            z-index: 0;
            width: 75%;
            background-color: rgb(228, 225, 225);
            border-radius: 10px;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .up {
            position: absolute;
            z-index: 2;
            top: -10%;
            left: -1%;
            height: 150px;
            width: 105%;
            background-color: rgb(228, 225, 225);
            transform: rotate(-3deg);
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .down {
            height: 70px;
        }

        .header {
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            color: rgb(0, 0, 0);
            background-color: rgb(247, 246, 246);
            padding: 30px 0 30px 0;
        }

        .code {
            padding: 1%;
            border-radius: 10px;
            width: 75%;
            color: rgb(169, 172, 173);
            background-color: rgb(255, 252, 252);
        }

        .value {
            font-size: 50px;
            color: rgb(56, 56, 56);
        }

        .footer {
            width: 75%;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<center>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="up"></div>
        <div class="header">
            <p>
            <h2>Code de confirmation</h2></p>
            <table role="presentation" border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="
    width: 75%;
    background-color: rgb(255, 252, 252);
    border-radius: 10px;
    color: rgb(169, 172, 173);
    padding: 10px;
    text-align: center;
">
                <tr>
                    <td style="padding: 10px;">
            <span style="
                font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
                font-size: 16px;
                color: rgb(169, 172, 173);
            ">Voici votre lien de confirmation</span>
                    </td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td style="padding: 10px;">
                        <p style="
                            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
                            font-size: 16px;
                            color: blue;
                            text-decoration: none;
                            display: inline-block;
                        ">
                            localhost:8080/utilisateur/signin/confirmation/<%= uid %>
                        </p>
                    </td>
                </tr>
            </table>
            <div class="footer">
                <p>Si cette requête ne vient pas de vous, changez immediatement votre mot de passe pour éviter des accès non autorisés</p>
            </div>
            <div class="code">
                <p>Voici votre code de confirmation</p>
                <h3 class="value"><%= codePin %></h3>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="down"></div>
    </div>
</center>
</body>
</html>